HEADWORD: Inoxidize
<hw>In*ox"i*dize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To prevent or
hinder oxidation, rust, or decay; <as>as, <ex>inoxidizing</ex> oils or
varnishes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inpatient</ent>⟦br⟧
